data.description: Welcome to 9031 Barley Loft Dr, a meticulously maintained 3-bed, 2.5-bath gem with a loft, built in 2002. Boasting 1,960 sqft, this home features newly remodeled bathrooms, a rare 5 ft. fenced yard with a patio for outdoor living, and a well-designed layout. Recent upgrades include a new roof (2018), HVAC (2020), Hot Water Tank (2021), and Stainless Steel Appliances (2022). Enjoy the perks of Columbus City Taxes with Olentangy Schools and a convenient location near schools, parks, shopping, and easy access to I-71. Your dream home awaits - act fast! Buyer to pay all closing costs.
